content: aur bhai kya chal raha hai

Arre, bhai, yeh toh aaj ki shaitaan ki raat hai, na? Udariyan aane se pehle hi barish aa gayi, aur ab toh taarif ke liye koi zaroorat nahin. Mere paas toh apne favorite Bollywood dialog mein kuch lines hai: "Chalti ka naam gaadi, aur main chalta hoon jeevan!" Bas, yeh hi feel hai na? Chal, kya aaj ke liye plans hai?
aryan bhai ka registration nahin hai vah kar rahe hain

Bhai, yeh toh aaj ki breaking news hai! Arya bhai ka registration toh shayad woh khud se kar lete hain, na? Kabhi-kabhi logon ko pata nahin chalta hai ki woh kya kar rahe hain, aur kabhi-kabhi toh pata chalta hai, lekin karna hi nahi chahte hain. Phir woh "Arey, aaj kal kya karne se?" ke dialogue ki wajah se sabko confuse karte hain.

Bhai, yeh toh maanaskaatmak hai! Ghanta samajhne mein mushkil ho rahi hai, toh kya hoga? Shayad aaj ke samay mein toh ghante ka kaam nahin, aur samajh ka kaam humein karna pad raha hai! Chalo, bhai, aaj ke liye ek kaam hua hai - humein samajhna hai ki Arya bhai ka registration kyun nahin hua. Arey, yeh toh mystery hai!
